# 🎨 legARTsy – YourART.YourLEGACY

**legARTsy** is a responsive, user-friendly art e-commerce and exhibition platform where users can explore, purchase, and manage curated artworks. It combines an elegant design with interactive features such as shopping, cart management, profile settings, and more.

---

## 📁 Project Structure
legARTsy/
├── Images # Pictures related to the website
├── Videos # Videos related to the website
├── index.html # Homepage
├── collections.html # Arts Collections
├── exhibitions.html # Exhibitions/Events
├── visit.html # Offline Store Info
├── cart.html # Shopping Cart
├── profile.html # User Profile
│
├── styles.css # Main stylesheet
├── script.js # JavaScript logic
├── README.md # You're here!


---

## 🚀 Features

- ✅ **Home Page Slider** — Rotating featured events or exhibitions
- 🛒 **Add to Cart** — Add artworks to cart with quantity and price tracking
- 💳 **Cart Page** — View items, total price, and clear cart option
- ⚙️ **User Profile Settings** — Set email notification & UI preferences
- 📱 **Responsive Design** — Works smoothly on desktop and mobile
- 🧩 **Navigation Menu** — Mobile-friendly toggleable menu

---

## 🛠️ Technologies Used

- **HTML5**
- **CSS3**
- **JavaScript**
- **LocalStorage API** – for persisting cart and preferences

